          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-5734 lnet: cleanup failed NI in lnet_startup_lndnis()",
        "message": "LU-5734 lnet: cleanup failed NI in lnet_startup_lndnis()\n\nIn lnet_dyn_add_ni(), if lnet_startup_lndnis() fails, then NI on the\nlocal &net_head list is freed.But lnet_startup_lndnis(&net_head) can\nfail after list_del(&ni->ni_list), i.e. after the NI has been removed\nalready from the &net_head. Clear up and free NI this these cases.\n\nSigned-off-by: Wang Shilong <wshilong@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I96a43798e744f821676c34a2e40f8b6a7494984f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
